Running from a command line

        R CMD BATCH --no-save Script-rjags.R

will create Figures 3 and 4 of the paper.

The output of running this command on our system is saved in the file
Script-rjags.Rout.orig.

Note that the file "PolMonCompactEven.bug" was derived from the file
"PolMonCompactEvenPred.bug" in the JAGS subdirectory by removing all
code related to computing prediction at additional specified x values.

